		<LocalizedStrings>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_DISTAL_PANCREATECTOMY</LocID>
				<Text>胰体尾切除术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_DISTAL_PANCREATECTOMY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>胰体尾切除术是切除胰腺远端（体尾部）部分的手术。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_FASCIOTOMY</LocID>
				<Text>筋膜切开术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_FASCIOTOMY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>筋膜切开术是一种切开筋膜以减轻肌肉筋膜室压力的手术，用于治疗急慢性筋膜室综合征。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_GASTRECTOMY</LocID>
				<Text>胃切除术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_GASTRECTOMY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>胃切除术是一种外科手术，切除全部或部分胃。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_LIVER_TRANSPLANT</LocID>
				<Text>肝移植</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_LIVER_TRANSPLANT_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>肝移植是以外科手术用另一个人的健康肝脏替换病变肝脏。可以移植整个肝脏，也可以只移植一部分。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_MYOTOMY</LocID>
				<Text>肌切开术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_MYOTOMY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>Heller肌切开术是一种外科手术，切开贲门肌肉，让食物和液体能够进入胃部。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_LAPAROSCOPY</LocID>
				<Text>腹腔镜手术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_LAPAROSCOPY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>一种微创外科技术。手术通过一系列小切口进行，将手术设备插入其中。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_SPLENECTOMY</LocID>
				<Text>脾切除术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_SPLENECTOMY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>脾切除术是切除脾脏的外科手术。脾脏是位于您左上腹肋骨下的一个器官。它有助于抵抗感染，并从血液中过滤掉不需要的物质，如衰老或受损的血细胞。脾切除术最常见的原因是治疗脾破裂，这通常是由腹部损伤引起的。脾切除术也可用于治疗其他疾病，包括引起不适的脾脏肿大（巨脾症）、一些血液疾病、某些癌症、感染以及非癌性囊肿或肿瘤。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_ENDOSCOPIC_CAUTERIZATION</LocID>
				<Text>内窥镜下烧灼术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_ENDOSCOPIC_CAUTERIZATION_DESCRIPTION</LocID>
				<Text>内窥镜下烧灼术是一种外科手术，利用电流烧灼某个区域以打开或封闭它。它通常用于在手术中止血。\n\n所需房间：诊断科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_AVM_RESECTION</LocID>
				<Text>动静脉畸形切除术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_AVM_RESECTION_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>动静脉畸形切除术需要将动静脉畸形从周围组织中精细分离。神经外科医生使用显微镜切断动静脉畸形的血液供应并将其切除。\n\n所需房间：神经外科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_HEMISPHERECTOMY</LocID>
				<Text>解剖性大脑半球切除术</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>
				<LocID>SUR_OL_HEMISPHERECTOMY_DESC</LocID>
				<Text>解剖性大脑半球切除术涉及物理切除大脑病变的半球，包括额叶、顶叶、颞叶和枕叶。大脑深部结构包括丘脑和基底节则被保留。\n\n所需房间：神经外科手术室。</Text>
			</GameDBLocalizedString>
		</LocalizedStrings>
	</GameDBStringTable>
